name: PathFinder
description:
“In the digital age and biotechnology,
aliens are predicted to be present in
the form of robots. In fact, some
believe that alien robots in the future
can be invited to cooperate by
humans. Humans will exist in a
post-biological era, where they will
coexist with extraterrestrial beings
and objects. When humans will work
with robots, aliens can also be
replaced with robots, but alien robots
will still not be able to have a sense of
empathy like a full human.. Therefore,
